    modelAnswer: "Use auto-scaling groups behind a load balancer. Stateless app servers — session in Redis. Read replicas for DB reads. CDN for static assets. Cache hot data in Redis. Queue async work. Pre-scale for known events (Black Friday). Use circuit breakers to shed load gracefully.",
